    v0 = (tmp - ((v0 + 0.26 + v0 + 0.00) * 0.31))

    tmp = 0.82
    v0 = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.26 + v1 + 0.49)) * 0.42)
    tmp = wp.exp(((tmp + 0.87 + v2 + 0.32) + (v1 + 0.50 * v0 + 0.77)))
